 Champions\", \"from\": 379, \"to\": 410}, {\"ngram\": \"table tennis\", \"from\": 414, \"to\": 426}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And recently he won the 39th Huawei National Table Tennis Championships in Kathmandu and also clinched gold for the first time in 7th National Games, Biratnagar.\", \"from\": 428, \"to\": 589, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 457, \"end\": 463, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huawei\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.794439565358926e-19, \"text\": \"Huawei\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huawei\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huawei\"}, {\"begin\": 479, \"end\": 485, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tennis\", \"score\": 0.9999995689609952, \"rank\": 4.3102423022763253e-07, \"text\": \"Tennis\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tennis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tennis\"}, {\"begin\": 503, \"end\": 512, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kathmandu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.078715494089562e-25, \"text\": \"Kathmandu\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kathmandu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kathmandu\"}, {\"begin\": 578, \"end\": 588, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Biratnagar\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.5798067443719385e-25, \"text\": \"Biratnagar\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Biratnagar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Biratnagar\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 531, \"to\": 535}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 540, \"to\": 554}, {\"ngram\": \"7th National Games\", \"from\": 558, \"to\": 576}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To add to his achievements, Santoo also won gold in the 36th National Table Tennis Championship, Kathmandu in 2014 under the Junior Boys Singles category, 10th late U-16 Hareram Joshi Memorial open Table Tennis Cham